      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.82,
      "size": 45072,
      "text": "比如三x加一，除以x减一再乘x加二，这个式子看着就让人头疼。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
