      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/split-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38160,
      "text": "如果分母是几个不同的一次因式相乘，就能拆成几个简单分式相加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "split",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "split-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/split-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "每个简单分式的分母，正是原来的一个一次因式。"
