    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "split",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "split-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/split-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "剩下的问题，就是求出每个分式头上的那个常数系数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "residue",
      "line_id": "res-1",
      "filename": "residue-res-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/residue-res-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "留数法非常巧妙：想求某个因式对应的系数，就把它从分母里盖住。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "residue",
      "line_id": "res-2",
      "filename": "residue-res-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/residue-res-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "再把这个因式的根代进剩下的式子，算出来的值就是系数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "residue",
      "line_id": "res-3",
      "filename": "residue-res-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/partial-fractions/xiaoxiao/residue-res-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.5,
      "size": 40032,
      "text": "写成公式就是，A等于分子在根处的值，除以分母求导在根处的值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "partial-fractions",
      "section_id": "verify",
